These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: metal, trance, d&b, soul, funk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
5 different games are played: domino, monopoly, mah-jongg, scrabble, billiard
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the fan of d&b is the fan of d&b##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
10. the fan of metal is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the fan of funk is between the person playing monopoly and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the person playing billiard is on the right of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Music-Genre      | metal        | trance | funk     | d&b   | soul |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Game   | scrabble  | monopoly     | domino | mah-jongg | billiard  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

