.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, september, november, july, august
5 different games are played: go, poker, monopoly, bridge, whist
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person playing go and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Birthday   | august    | september       | november      | march | july        |
| Game   | whist   | poker     | go    | bridge  | monopoly     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

