.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, taxi, car, scooter, trike
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, white, azure, black, green
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person who likes black is in the middle##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who likes green##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
13. the person who likes green is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Transport   | car      | taxi      | scooter       | trike       | tram       |
| Color         | white | green  | black    | blood-red    | azure        |

