The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
5 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla, fish, bird, ferret
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is between the fan of reggae and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the owner of the snake##1
11. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
| City         | rome | boston    | hamburg  | hannover | san-francisco   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Pet   | chinchilla    | fish | bird | ferret | snake   |

