 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's sport is golf and the person traveling to colone##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| City       | hannover | rome | colone  | marseilles | paris    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Birthday   | november       | december      | august      | july | september  |

