.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
City: paris, marseilles, new-york, hamburg, london
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
There are 5 different favourite colors: purple, lilac, lavender, pink, apricot
 1. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person watching crime movies and the person traveling to new-york##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person traveling to london and the person who likes lilac##2
 7. the person who likes pink is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
10. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| City           | marseilles | new-york | hamburg | london    | paris  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Color   | lavender  | lilac        | purple   | pink    | apricot     |

