.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, cola, juice, hot-chocolate
5 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, snooker, poker, domino
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person playing canasta##2
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person driving the airplane and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
 9. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | card-games |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | juice    | lemonade | hot-chocolate | cola      |
| Game           | snooker | scrabble    | canasta       | poker     | domino      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

