.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, domino, whist, poker
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, taxi, scooter, motorbike, tram
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the person driving the tram is between the malaysian and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 4. the person driving the tram is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the thai and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person playing whist is the fan of blues##1
 9. the american is the fan of blues##1
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Game         | domino    | poker  | mah-jongg  | backgammon      | whist |
| Transport   | taxi    | tram   | motorbike | scooter | trike   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 